<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AccuflexPro - Accounting Experts</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8f8ff, #e6ecf0);
      color: #333;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #004080, #0066cc);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.3em;
    }
    nav {
      background: #003366;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 15px;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffcc00;
    }
    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #004080;
    }
    .services {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    .card h3 {
      color: #004080;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .card p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    footer {
      background: #002244;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>AccuflexPro</h1>
    <p>Professional Accounting & GST Services Across India</p>
  </header>
  <nav>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <section id="services">
    <h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
    <div class="services">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>GST Compliance</h3>
        <p>Filing GSTR-1, 3B, 9, and audits with full reconciliation and expert assistance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Accounting & Bookkeeping</h3>
        <p>End-to-end bookkeeping and ledger services tailored to your business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Income Tax Returns</h3>
        <p>Preparation and filing of ITRs for individuals, firms, and corporations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Startup & Business Setup</h3>
        <p>Assistance with company registration, PAN, TAN, and tax advisory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: auto; font-size: 1.1em; text-align: center;">
      AccuflexPro is committed to delivering top-tier financial services with an emphasis on accuracy, compliance, and client satisfaction. Based in India, we serve clients across industries with modern tools and professional integrity.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em;">
      📧 Email: contact@accuflexpro.com<br>
      📞 Phone: +91-98765-43210<br>
      📍 Location: Chandigarh, India
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 AccuflexPro | Built with passion for Indian businesses 💼
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
